.. -*- restructuredtext -*-

cloud_sptheme is a nice sphinx theme, with some associated sphinx extensions.

The latest documentation can be found online `XXX`.

Requirements
-----------
* Sphinx 1.0 or newer

Installation
------------
To install from source using ``setup.py``::

   python setup.py build
   sudo python setup.py install

For more detailed installation & testing instructions, see "docs/install.rst",

Online Resources
----------------
* **Homepage & Source:** `<https://bitbucket.org/ecollins/cloud_sptheme/src>`_
* **Docs:** `<https://packages.python.org/cloud_sptheme>`_
* **PyPI:** `<http://pypi.python.org/cloud_sptheme>`_
